code: @Test public void testCustomErrorPath() {     @SuppressWarnings("rawtypes")     ResponseEntity<Map> entity = this.restTemplate.withBasicAuth("user", getPassword()).getForEntity("/oops", Map.class).     assertThat(entity.getStatusCode()).isEqualTo(HttpStatus.INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR).     @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")     Map<String, Object> body = entity.getBody().     assertThat(body.get("error")).isEqualTo("None").     assertThat(body.get("status")).isEqualTo(999). }

@Test public void testCustomContextPath() {     ResponseEntity<String> entity = this.restTemplate.withBasicAuth("user", getPassword()).getForEntity("/admin/health", String.class).     assertThat(entity.getStatusCode()).isEqualTo(HttpStatus.OK).     assertThat(entity.getBody()).contains("\"status\":\"UP\"").     assertThat(entity.getBody()).contains("\"hello\":\"world\""). }
